---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Approach — RADIANX CAPITAL"
  description="A disciplined four-step methodology: discovery, architecture, execution and ongoing stewardship."
  currentPath="/approach"
>



<!-- PAGE HEADER -->
<header class="ph">
  <div class="ph-atm"></div>
  <div class="ph-watermark">Method.</div>
  <div class="ph-geo">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 900" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" fill="none">
      <g transform="translate(1160,460)">
        <g class="rot">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="300" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.022)" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M0,-300 A300,300 0 0,1 212,212" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.05)" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="0" cy="-300" r="4" fill="rgba(240,238,235,.15)"/>
        </g>
        <g class="rotr">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="370" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.012)" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="3,9"/>
        </g>
      </g>
      <g transform="translate(200,200)">
        <g class="rotr">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="80" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.04)" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M0,-80 A80,80 0 0,1 56,56" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.1)" stroke-width="1.2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="ph-inner">
    <div class="sec-tag rv">How We Think</div>
    <h1 class="ph-h rv">
      Discipline over<br><em>impulse.</em> Always.
    </h1>
    <div class="ph-cols rv">
      <p class="ph-col-body">
        Our approach to wealth management is grounded in a single conviction: that consistent, disciplined process produces better outcomes than reactive judgment. Every decision we make on behalf of a client is governed by a structured methodology — not by market sentiment, not by intuition, and never by short-term thinking.
      </p>
      <p class="ph-col-body">
        We apply this framework uniformly across every engagement — from a client with $500K in investable assets to one managing a multi-generational family office. The rigor does not vary. The attention does not vary. The standard does not vary.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- PHILOSOPHY STRIP -->
<div class="phil-strip">
  <div class="ps rv">
    <p class="ps-q">"The goal of investing is not to minimise risk. It is to take only the risks worth taking."</p>
    <div class="ps-attr">Investment Philosophy · RADIANX CAPITAL</div>
  </div>
  <div class="ps rv d1">
    <p class="ps-q">"A financial plan that cannot survive a bear market was never a financial plan."</p>
    <div class="ps-attr">Planning Philosophy · RADIANX CAPITAL</div>
  </div>
  <div class="ps rv d2">
    <p class="ps-q">"Transparency is not a feature of good advice. It is a precondition for it."</p>
    <div class="ps-attr">Client Philosophy · RADIANX CAPITAL</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STEPS -->
<section class="steps-section">

  <!-- STEP 01 -->
  <div class="step-row rv">
    <div class="step-num-col">
      <div class="step-count">01</div>
      <div class="step-index">01 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 04 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Discovery</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2 class="step-title">Deep<br><em>Discovery</em></h2>
      <p class="step-body">
        We begin every engagement with a structured discovery process that goes well beyond a standard financial questionnaire. We want to understand not just your balance sheet, but the full context of your financial life — your income structure, your obligations, your family dynamics, your tax exposure, your timeline, and — critically — what financial security actually means to you.
      </p>
      <p class="step-body" style="margin-top:16px">
        This conversation is unhurried. We do not rush toward recommendations. We ask questions that most advisers don't ask, because the quality of our advice depends entirely on the quality of our understanding.
      </p>
      <div class="step-badge">Duration: 1 – 2 Sessions</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-detail">
      <div class="sd-list">
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Financial Life Audit</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Complete review of assets, liabilities, income sources, insurance coverage, tax history, and existing accounts.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Goal Mapping</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Structured conversation about short, medium, and long-term objectives — retirement, education, estate, lifestyle, and legacy.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Risk Profiling</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Quantitative and qualitative assessment of risk tolerance, capacity, and required return — not a five-question online questionnaire.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Adviser Fit Assessment</div>
            <div class="sd-d">An honest determination of whether RADIANX CAPITAL is the right partner for your specific situation and expectations.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 02 -->
  <div class="step-row rv">
    <div class="step-num-col">
      <div class="step-count">02</div>
      <div class="step-index">02 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 04 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Architecture</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2 class="step-title">Strategic<br><em>Architecture</em></h2>
      <p class="step-body">
        Once we have a complete picture of your situation, we design a comprehensive financial strategy — a coordinated, integrated plan that addresses every relevant dimension of your financial life simultaneously. This is not a product recommendation dressed up as a plan. It is a genuine architectural document: a blueprint for your financial future.
      </p>
      <p class="step-body" style="margin-top:16px">
        Investment strategy, tax efficiency, estate structure, retirement income, and protection planning are not treated as separate silos. They are designed as a single, coherent system — because that is what they are.
      </p>
      <div class="step-badge">Duration: 1 – 3 Weeks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-detail">
      <div class="sd-list">
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Investment Policy Statement</div>
            <div class="sd-d">A written document defining your investment objectives, constraints, asset allocation, and benchmarks — the governing charter of your portfolio.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Tax Architecture</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Integrated tax strategy across accounts — asset location, harvesting methodology, conversion analysis, and charitable giving framework.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Estate & Protection Structure</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Recommended trust structures, beneficiary alignment, and insurance framework — coordinated with your legal advisers.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Scenario Analysis</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Stress-testing your plan against market drawdowns, longevity risk, inflation, tax law changes, and major life events.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 03 -->
  <div class="step-row rv">
    <div class="step-num-col">
      <div class="step-count">03</div>
      <div class="step-index">03 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 04 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Execution</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2 class="step-title">Precise<br><em>Execution</em></h2>
      <p class="step-body">
        Strategy without execution is fiction. Once your financial architecture is approved, we implement it with institutional discipline — every position established deliberately, every tax implication considered, every account structured correctly from inception.
      </p>
      <p class="step-body" style="margin-top:16px">
        We coordinate with your custodians, tax professionals, attorneys, and other advisers to ensure that implementation is seamless and that nothing falls through the gaps. You should not have to manage the complexity of your own wealth management. That is precisely what we are here for.
      </p>
      <div class="step-badge">Duration: 2 – 6 Weeks</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-detail">
      <div class="sd-list">
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Portfolio Construction</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Deliberate, tax-aware establishment of every position according to your Investment Policy Statement — no shortcuts, no approximations.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Account Consolidation & Transfer</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Efficient transition of existing accounts — in-kind where advantageous, liquidated and reinvested where required — with full tax analysis.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Professional Coordination</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Structured handoff points with your CPA, estate attorney, and any other professionals involved in your financial life.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Client Onboarding</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Clear communication at every step — you will always know what has been done, what is pending, and what comes next.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 04 -->
  <div class="step-row rv">
    <div class="step-num-col">
      <div class="step-count">04</div>
      <div class="step-index">04 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 04 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Ongoing Review</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h2 class="step-title">Continuous<br><em>Stewardship</em></h2>
      <p class="step-body">
        The most important thing we do at RADIANX CAPITAL is not the onboarding — it is what happens afterward. Wealth management is not a transaction. It is an ongoing discipline that requires continuous attention, proactive adaptation, and a deep understanding of how your life and the world around you are changing.
      </p>
      <p class="step-body" style="margin-top:16px">
        We monitor your portfolio daily. We review your plan formally at least annually. We reach out proactively when something in the market, in the tax code, or in your life demands a response — not because you called us, but because that is what a genuine fiduciary does.
      </p>
      <div class="step-badge">Ongoing · No Fixed Term</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-detail">
      <div class="sd-list">
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Daily Portfolio Monitoring</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Continuous oversight of portfolio risk, performance attribution, and positioning — with proactive rebalancing when thresholds are breached.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Annual Plan Review</div>
            <div class="sd-d">A thorough, structured review of your complete financial plan — updated for life changes, regulatory developments, and shifting goals.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Tax-Year Planning</div>
            <div class="sd-d">Year-round tax coordination — harvesting, conversion analysis, distribution planning, and CPA collaboration before year-end.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sd">
          <div class="sd-dash">—</div>
          <div>
            <div class="sd-t">Proactive Communication</div>
            <div class="sd-d">You hear from us when something matters. Not quarterly newsletter fluff — substantive communication tied to your specific situation.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<!-- PRINCIPLES -->
<section class="principles">
  <div class="prin-bg">Rigour.</div>
  <div class="prin-inner">
    <div class="prin-head">
      <div>
        <div class="sec-tag rv">What Guides Us</div>
        <h2 class="rv" style="font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(34px,3.5vw,52px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-.3px">The principles<br>behind the <em>method</em></h2>
      </div>
      <p class="rv" style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:var(--white2);line-height:1.82;padding-top:52px">
        Every firm has a stated process. What distinguishes a firm is the principles that govern how that process is applied — especially under pressure, especially when the easy path and the right path diverge.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="prin-grid">
      <div class="pr rv">
        <div class="pr-top"></div>
        <div class="pr-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
            <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="14" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
            <path d="M18 4 A14 14 0 0 1 32 18" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.6)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="3" fill="rgba(240,238,235,.4)"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-t">Process Over Prediction</div>
        <div class="pr-d">We do not build strategies around market forecasts. We build strategies robust enough to perform well across a wide range of futures — because no one knows which future will materialise.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr rv d1">
        <div class="pr-top"></div>
        <div class="pr-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
            <rect x="6" y="10" width="24" height="18" rx="1.5" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
            <path d="M6 16h24" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
            <path d="M12 22h12" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.6)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-t">Tax as Strategy</div>
        <div class="pr-d">Tax planning is not an afterthought layered on top of investment management. It is a first-order consideration in every allocation decision, every rebalancing trade, every distribution.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr rv d2">
        <div class="pr-top"></div>
        <div class="pr-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
            <path d="M8 26 L14 18 L20 22 L26 14 L32 18" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.6)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <circle cx="26" cy="14" r="2.5" fill="rgba(240,238,235,.3)"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-t">Long Time Horizons</div>
        <div class="pr-d">Wealth is built over decades. We evaluate every decision through a long-term lens — resisting the pull of recency bias, narrative investing, and quarter-to-quarter performance anxiety.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr rv">
        <div class="pr-top"></div>
        <div class="pr-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
            <path d="M18 6L28 11v10l-10 7-10-7V11L18 6z" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.2)" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M18 6L28 11v10l-10 7-10-7V11L18 6z" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.5)" stroke-width="1" fill="rgba(240,238,235,.04)"/>
            <path d="M13 19l3 3 7-7" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.7)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-t">Fiduciary Without Exception</div>
        <div class="pr-d">Every recommendation — every trade, every product, every allocation — is evaluated solely against the question: is this in the best interest of this specific client at this specific moment?</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr rv d1">
        <div class="pr-top"></div>
        <div class="pr-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
            <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="7" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.4)" stroke-width="1"/>
            <circle cx="22" cy="22" r="7" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.2)" stroke-width="1"/>
            <path d="M17.5 17.5 A7 7 0 0 0 22 15 A7 7 0 0 0 19 22.5" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.3)" stroke-width="1" fill="rgba(240,238,235,.04)"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-t">Integrated Thinking</div>
        <div class="pr-d">Investment, tax, estate, retirement, and cash flow planning are one system. We manage them that way — with every decision informed by its implications across all dimensions of your financial life.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pr rv d2">
        <div class="pr-top"></div>
        <div class="pr-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none">
            <path d="M8 18h4l4-8 4 16 4-10 4 2" stroke="rgba(240,238,235,.6)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="pr-t">Evidence Over Narrative</div>
        <div class="pr-d">We are skeptical of investment stories, thematic trends, and market narratives. We follow the evidence — quantitative analysis, historical context, and first-principles reasoning over compelling stories.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DIFFERENCE -->
<section class="diff">
  <div>
    <div class="sec-tag rv">The Distinction</div>
    <h2 class="diff-h rv">What makes<br>our approach <em>different</em></h2>
    <p class="diff-body rv">
      Most wealth management firms describe a similar process. Discover, plan, implement, review. The difference is not the steps — it is the standard to which each step is held, and the principles that govern what happens inside them.
    </p>
    <p class="diff-body rv">
      At RADIANX CAPITAL, the standard is institutional. The obligation is fiduciary. The attention is personal. And the commitment to every client relationship is long-term.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="diff-rows rv">
    <!-- Header row -->
    <div class="diff-row" style="background:none;border:1px solid var(--brd)">
      <div class="drc-head">RADIANX CAPITAL</div>
      <div class="drc-head">Typical Advisory Firm</div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row">
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Client Relationship</div>
        <div class="drc-val">Long-term partnership, selective client roster</div>
      </div>
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Client Relationship</div>
        <div class="drc-val dim">Volume-driven, high client-to-adviser ratio</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row">
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Portfolio Construction</div>
        <div class="drc-val">Built from scratch for each client</div>
      </div>
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Portfolio Construction</div>
        <div class="drc-val dim">Model portfolios applied broadly</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row">
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Tax Integration</div>
        <div class="drc-val">Embedded in every investment decision</div>
      </div>
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Tax Integration</div>
        <div class="drc-val dim">Addressed separately, if at all</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row">
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Compensation Structure</div>
        <div class="drc-val">Fee-only, no commissions, no referral fees</div>
      </div>
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Compensation Structure</div>
        <div class="drc-val dim">Often commission-based or hybrid</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row">
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Communication</div>
        <div class="drc-val">Proactive, substantive, situation-specific</div>
      </div>
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Communication</div>
        <div class="drc-val dim">Reactive, templated, calendar-driven</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-row">
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Fiduciary Standard</div>
        <div class="drc-val">Always, legally, without exception</div>
      </div>
      <div class="drc">
        <div class="drc-label">Fiduciary Standard</div>
        <div class="drc-val dim">Variable — suitability standard only</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FIDUCIARY COMMITMENT -->
<section class="fiduciary">
  <div class="fid-geo">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 600 600" fill="none">
      <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="240" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
      <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="180" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,8"/>
      <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="120" stroke="white" stroke-width="1"/>
      <path d="M300,60 A240,240 0 0,1 540,300" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <circle cx="300" cy="60" r="6" fill="white"/>
      <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="8" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="fid-inner">
    <div class="fid-tag rv">Our Commitment</div>
    <h2 class="fid-h rv">The fiduciary<br>standard is not<br>a <em>differentiator.</em><br>It is the baseline.</h2>
    <p class="fid-body rv">
      We find it remarkable that the fiduciary standard — the legal requirement to act in a client's best interest — is treated as a distinguishing feature in the wealth management industry. It should be the floor, not the ceiling.
    </p>
    <p class="fid-body rv">
      At RADIANX CAPITAL, we meet the fiduciary standard because it is legally required of us as an SEC-registered investment adviser. But our commitment to our clients goes beyond what is legally mandated — it reflects a genuine belief that the only acceptable way to manage another person's wealth is with complete loyalty to their interests.
    </p>
    <div class="fid-rule"></div>
    <p class="fid-legal rv">
      RADIANX CAPITAL, LLC is registered with the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission as an investment adviser under the Investment Advisers Act of 1940 (CRD# 298178 · SEC# 801-117100). SEC registration requires the firm to adhere to fiduciary standards of conduct in all client interactions. Investment advice involves risk including the possible loss of principal.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="cta-geo">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 360 360" fill="none">
      <circle cx="180" cy="180" r="150" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" fill="none"/>
      <path d="M180,30 A150,150 0 0,1 330,180" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <circle cx="180" cy="30" r="5" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <h2 class="cta-h rv">
    Precision begins<br>with the<br><em>first conversation.</em>
  </h2>
  <div class="cta-r rv">
    <p class="cta-body">
      You have seen how we think. Now let us apply that thinking to your situation. A complimentary initial consultation is available to all qualified prospective clients — no obligation, no pressure.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->

</div>

</Layout>

<style is:global>

/* ═══ PAGE HEADER ═══ */
.ph{
  padding:200px 60px 120px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--brd);
  min-height:88vh;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;
}
.ph-atm{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.ph-atm::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-5%;right:-8%;width:55%;height:70%;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 65% 25%,rgba(122,150,168,.04) 0%,transparent 65%)}
.ph-atm::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-10%;left:-5%;width:45%;height:55%;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 80%,rgba(15,18,40,.5) 0%,transparent 60%)}
.ph-geo{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.ph-geo svg{width:100%;height:100%}

/* Large number watermark */
.ph-watermark{
  position:absolute;right:-20px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-55%);
  font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(200px,28vw,380px);
  font-weight:300;font-style:italic;
  color:rgba(240,238,235,.022);letter-spacing:-10px;
  pointer-events:none;z-index:0;line-height:1;
  user-select:none;
}

.ph-inner{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:900px}
